name: Indiana Secretary of State Holli Sullivan
tweet: We're several weeks away, but I wanted to take this time to remind you that Monday, April 4th is Indiana's voter registration deadline.   If you still need to register or are unsure about your voting status, please visit our voter portal:  https://t.co/H9HUDBMtrC

name: Indiana Secretary of State Holli Sullivan
tweet: My office is serious about making sure all Hoosiers’ votes are secure and accurately counted. Our voting machines are protected against cyber attacks through the use of intrusion detection and prevention systems. #VoteIN  https://t.co/ynRN6MXeV3

name: Indiana Secretary of State Holli Sullivan
tweet: I offer my deepest condolences to the family, friends and loved ones of Capt. Matthew Tomkiewicz. I am thankful our nation and our state produce heroes like Capt. Tomkiewicz. His service and sacrifice will not be forgotten.

name: Indiana Secretary of State Holli Sullivan
tweet: It was great to connect with Clerk Lisa Witt during my visit to Fayette County! I am thankful to live in a state where we have clerks who are dedicated to conducting secure elections that Hoosiers can trust.   https://t.co/qDB5TRO29b

name: Indiana Secretary of State Holli Sullivan
tweet: Thanks to our media partners for helping spread the word about the wonderful things we are doing to further secure Indiana’s voting process and boost confidence.   Equipment like VVPATs will ensure that every vote in Indiana has a paper trail by the next presidential election.  https://t.co/ypuPHW7l4E

name: Indiana Secretary of State Holli Sullivan
tweet: My legislation that improves voter confidence by providing more paper audit trails, enhanced cybersecurity protection, and safeguards digital requests for absentee ballots has been signed into law.   https://t.co/S5eyKWo4td

name: Indiana Secretary of State Holli Sullivan
tweet: As I wrap up my 92 County tour, it has been a truly wonderful experience having the opportunity to travel the state and get to know our county clerks. Thank you for all that you do to safeguard Indiana's elections!  https://t.co/b4ikbMhsp5

name: Indiana Secretary of State Holli Sullivan
tweet: As your Secretary of State, it has been my goal to provide Hoosiers with tangible results. I am proud of all that we have accomplished during my first year in office and wanted to share with you some of the highlights.  https://t.co/uZvlqdc6Ko

name: Indiana Secretary of State Holli Sullivan
tweet: As I reflect on my first year in office, I would like to say it has been an honor to serve as your 62nd Secretary of State. My office and all its divisions are dedicated to providing great government service and creating a better Indiana for all Hoosiers!  https://t.co/uNve7RpamO

name: Indiana Secretary of State Holli Sullivan
tweet: I am thankful for the Indiana General Assembly's dedication to election security. My legislation that improves voter confidence by providing more paper audit trails and safeguards digital requests for absentee ballots has been signed into law.  https://t.co/zD5hPSsCOt
